#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.interleave"
msgstr "# triton.language.interleave"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:4
msgid "将两个相同形状的输入张量在最后一个维度上交错排列，输出张量的最后一个维度大小为输入张量的2倍，其他维度保持不变。"
msgstr "Interleave two input tensors of the same shape along the last dimension. The size of the last dimension of the output tensor is twice that of the input tensors, while the other dimensions remain unchanged."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.interleave(x, y)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `x.interleave(y)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.interleave(x, y)` - function call form\n"
"- `x.interleave(y)` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:12
msgid ""
"- 将两个相同形状的输入张量在最后一个维度上交错排列\n"
"- 输出张量的最后一个维度大小为输入张量的2倍\n"
"- 其他维度保持不变\n"
msgstr ""
"- Interleave two input tensors of the same shape along the last dimension\n"
"- The last dimension of the output tensor is twice the size of the input tensors\n"
"- Other dimensions remain unchanged\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| x | tensor | 是 | 第一个输入张量 |\n"
"| y | tensor | 是 | 第二个输入张量，形状必须与x相同 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| x | tensor | Yes | The first input tensor |\n"
"| y | tensor | Yes | The second input tensor, shape must be the same as x |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 输入形状的最后一个维度乘以2\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 交替排列x和y的元素\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** The last dimension of the input shape multiplied by 2\n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Memory layout:** Interleaved arrangement of x and y elements\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:26
msgid ""
"- 两个输入张量必须具有相同的形状和数据类型\n"
"- 输出张量的形状为输入形状的最后一个维度乘以2\n"
msgstr ""
"- The two input tensors must have the same shape and data type  \n"
"- The shape of the output tensor is the last dimension of the input shape multiplied by 2\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:28
msgid "### 2.2 DataType支持表"
msgstr "### 2.2 DataType Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/interleave.md:30
msgid ""
"| 支持情况 | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU支持 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Support Status | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
